eplyTime":"2018-06-28T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"響香港，調酒員=水吧佬、洗杯佬、古喱生啤佬、雪啤酒員、搬雪佬。<br />\n好多投資者唔會當係一門專業<br />\n冇人識欣賞cocktial<br />\n就算酒店做都係咁話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"連台灣日本都比唔上<br />\n唔好講英國了"},{"pid":"6b9bb517b5b7a0402004eb0233733d4e3aeca79d","tid":721301,"uid":19973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到呢個post<br />\n先醒起曾經我既夢想都係成為一個bartender<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>想做就去做嘛，唔好令自己人生同咸魚無分別</blockquote><br />\n你要加油就真 日夜顛倒既生活唔易過<br />\n好想有機會去銀座啲酒吧飲下 望下認真既調酒師到底會係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3a344fb4949a91640fd1c2ab75db7c643d4e58","tid":721301,"uid":112709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dafa072106d2357f9ae8f67bbc9342aacde38220","tid":721301,"uid":4247,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"響香港，調酒員=水吧佬、洗杯佬、古喱生啤佬、雪啤酒員、搬雪佬。<br />\n好多投資者唔會當係一門專業<br />\n冇人識欣賞cocktial<br />\n就算酒店做都係咁話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"無錯，我以前做餐廳Bar，每次聽個廢中經理話&quot;你地水吧呢啲野好普通姐，求其搵個人來學都得啦&quot;，話個個都學到已經無咩野，聽到佢講水吧兩個字即刻想沖埋去爆鳩佢樽。<br />\n<br />\n清Bar就會好啲，叫做你會有返比人尊重嘅感覺。"},{"pid":"e119b0de3f0ce7c8904a63e1ed6eb4050a47cead","tid":721301,"uid":112709,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b9bb517b5b7a0402004eb0233733d4e3aeca79d","tid":721301,"uid":19973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到呢個post<br />\n先醒起曾經我既夢想都係成為一個bartender<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>想做就去做嘛，唔好令自己人生同咸魚無分別</blockquote><br />\n你要加油就真 日夜顛倒既生活唔易過<br />\n好想有機會去銀座啲酒吧飲下 望下認真既調酒師到底會係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"賣醉做樹窿嘅感覺太正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身又係夜貓唔中意早訓，機緣巧合就做埋吧聽打。同埋我個人會覺得做呢行日日對唔同嘅人，做唔同嘅野係幾充實嘅一件事。姐係算好過我好似以前Intern日日坐office做同樣野，仲要玩埋辦公室政治，長期咁搞真係會痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係我個人感覺，無針對其他人意思，職業無分貴賤，不喜勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rwCbUPAVdt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrwCbUPAVdt8&d=RYqZaRrScIHxWGlkNoPyFQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ae76f7ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rwCbUPAVdt8</a><br />\nBTW，日本啲Bartender雕冰都好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636393942c3adc45d5df7200338fc282c6b02b9c","tid":721301,"uid":112709,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fa13ae0bf9be73da17f36b6443e58dbabf0a021","tid":721301,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dafa072106d2357f9ae8f67bbc9342aacde38220","tid":721301,"uid":4247,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"響香港，調酒員=水吧佬、洗杯佬、古喱生啤佬、雪啤酒員、搬雪佬。<br />\n好多投資者唔會當係一門專業<br />\n冇人識欣賞cocktial<br />\n就算酒店做都係咁話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"連台灣日本都比唔上<br />\n唔好講英國了"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"應該話香港呢個文化沙漠好多野都無比人當過專業去尊重<br />\n<br />\n我同時係好欣賞咖啡師同廚師，但講真完全無feel過大部份香港人有尊重過佢地<br />\n(有時望到啲餐廳落場，啲廚師要鋪紙皮訓地下個心都唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"4413a07ccdc654b64498ebc0d22d5783721293b0","tid":721301,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636393942c3adc45d5df7200338fc282c6b02b9c","tid":721301,"uid":112709,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fa13ae0bf9be73da17f36b6443e58dbabf0a021","tid":721301,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dafa072106d2357f9ae8f67bbc9342aacde38220","tid":721301,"uid":4247,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"響香港，調酒員=水吧佬、洗杯佬、古喱生啤